20:43.327 --> 20:44.535
What's the verdict?

20:44.535 --> 20:47.246
Well, we considered
the basic model,

20:47.246 --> 20:52.126
but I--I think we're gonna go
with the Eternity Elite.

20:52.126 --> 20:53.127
Wonderful.

20:53.127 --> 20:56.465
♪♪♪

20:56.465 --> 20:59.468
On second thought, maybe we
should take another look

20:59.468 --> 21:01.511
at the no-frills model.

21:01.511 --> 21:04.347
You know, I mean the, uh,

21:04.347 --> 21:07.850
the workmanship is, um,
it's substandard.

21:07.850 --> 21:09.394
Nope, it's not gonna work.

21:09.394 --> 21:12.356
So all we need is
your credit card, dear.

21:12.356 --> 21:13.314
[sighs]

21:13.314 --> 21:14.607
Now, aren't you comfortable?

21:14.607 --> 21:16.109
[sighs] This is amazing.

21:16.109 --> 21:17.902
Look at this workmanship.

21:17.902 --> 21:20.029
It's a good color on you too.

21:20.029 --> 21:23.700
