23:03.591 --> 23:06.093
Well, you know you always have
our place if you need it.

23:06.093 --> 23:08.221
Looks like your inn
is all booked up.

23:08.221 --> 23:09.764
Ooh!
Just say the word,

23:09.764 --> 23:11.558
I'll kick those refugee kids'
asses to the curb.

23:11.558 --> 23:12.391
It's okay, I don't
need a place.

23:12.391 --> 23:14.685
Debbie, if these--

23:14.685 --> 23:16.687
I'm just gonna get the family
I work for to let me stay.

23:16.687 --> 23:17.980
- I can take Carl.
- Yeah, you can.

23:17.980 --> 23:19.774
All eight inches.

23:19.774 --> 23:20.817
I'm pimping like that.

23:20.817 --> 23:22.610
- Feel me?
