of this little minstrel act.

23:28.617 --> 23:30.535
You think cornrows
make you black?

23:30.535 --> 23:32.537
400 years of oppression
makes you black,

23:32.537 --> 23:34.872
and if you keep up
with this wigger bullshit,

23:34.872 --> 23:37.291
