23:44.423 --> 23:45.591
Yeah, you can stay
at my apartment.

23:45.591 --> 23:47.426
That could work.

23:47.426 --> 23:51.180
It might be a little tight, but
I think we could fit everyone.

23:51.180 --> 23:52.890
